cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.IT

This paper deals with image and video recognition, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses statistical distribution and kernelized linear dynamic systems, which are topics related to machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of dissimilarity measures and convergence analysis suggests information theory (cs.IT) as another possible sub-category. Finally, the mention of dynamic scenes and textures indicates multimedia (cs.MM) as a relevant sub-category.
